{"tid":1261244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"灰狗英文全名係咩？","createTime":"2019-06-27T06:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T06:44:14.000Z","uid":268905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9806dec9a35cf8d5f27d2361206097cd9cf5e93b","tid":1261244,"uid":268905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"起到條友英文全名未？<br />\n<br />\n大家可以send email/填form去警務處公開資料主任度攞灰狗更表，睇下佢26-27號番咩更。<br />\n<br />\n公務員朋友話有全名就可以問，因為更表係pre-exiting document，佢地無得懶Admin burden，10日內要回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.access.gov.hk/tc/howtomakeinfo/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.access.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhowtomakeinfo%2Findex.html&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0di9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=35dab511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.access.gov.hk/tc/howtomakeinfo/index.html</a> <br />\n揀番警務處就有email address<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e7efcf81ff235ddf58935a7d694562b931e323","tid":1261244,"uid":161541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"推到發現警狗講大話"}]}